                     verfallen sein.</rs>
                  <rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_729_men_2">Der Spruch geschah in Gegenwart <rs type="person" ref="#pe__michael_salicher_QGW_II_I_729"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Michels des Salicher, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__traiskirchen">vicari</roleName> dacz Dreschirchen</rs> <rs type="person" ref="#pe__niklas_QGW_II_I_729"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Niclas, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__lichtenstein">chaplan</roleName> ze Liechtenstain</rs> <rs type="person" ref="#pe__friedrich_chamschilt_QGW_II_I_729">Fridreichen des Chamschilt</rs>
